data.description: Embrace resort-style living on this sprawling 6-acre estate in North Bend Valley. This fully remodeled residence, boasting 3 beds and 2 baths, is cocooned by a neighborhood of multi-million-dollar homes. Revel in breathtaking Mt Si views and take a refreshing dip in the inviting in-ground pool with its private pool house. The property also features a host of amenities including outbuildings, a barn, carports, a greenhouse, and a workshop. New appliances add a modern touch to this serene escape, just moments from town with easy access to I-90, Issaquah, and Seattle.
